{"tid":2275841,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12港人其中一位不願曝光之女友: 願你早日平安歸來 你就是我一生的幸福","createTime":"2020-11-07T12:49:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T03:24:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":117,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"cc6d060f2ca0a7409de894bee7a3797e3f13faa8","tid":2275841,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/123411011_173648411142256_7657782441715972848_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=-w7HVAxsFsMAX9d5ZH1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;oh=ad761fd3fd4084869885aee530ab1f43&amp;oe=5FCDA527\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F123411011_173648411142256_7657782441715972848_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3D-w7HVAxsFsMAX9d5ZH1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26oh%3Dad761fd3fd4084869885aee530ab1f43%26oe%3D5FCDA527&h=dc8be5bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【幸福】<br />\n<br />\n「我係12港人其中一位不願曝光之女友，希望大家能夠體諒或明白。<br />\n<br />\n我地識於微時 關係由好朋友昇華至情侶。<br />\n<br />\n認識他的人都清楚知道，他每一天都會好好珍惜時光，每一天都會好好愛錫我，保護我，甚至交帶一些朋友們照顧我，因為他唔確定何年何月要受到不公平的審訊，再一次步入監房。<br />\n<br />\n他待我在朋友眼中係一個好浪漫好甜好暖的男朋友，而我在他眼中便是一生中最愛。<br />\n<br />\n今日係他離開第77日，每一日都期昐著有他的消息，不論是好是壞只求有消息。<br />\n<br />\n昨日再一次舊地重遊，去懷念我們的苦與甜，回憶一一浮現在眼前，但我知道我們仍然可以手拖手步向屬於我們倆口子的將來。<br />\n<br />\n面對種種的打壓甚至未知的刑期，我都願意等你，你曾經講過可能10年或20年後再見，寧願我放棄你去追尋一生的幸福，我好想你知道：你就是我一生中的幸福。<br />\n<br />\n最後我好想透過關注組多謝他的朋友/兄弟姐妹一直支持我陪伴我，亦好多謝你為我所做的一切。<br />\n<br />\n#願你早日平安歸來<br />\n#你就是我一生的幸福 」<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n#BringThemBack<br />\n#save12hkyouths<br />\n#save12<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/save12hkyouths/photos/a.112567073917057/173648407808923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsave12hkyouths%2Fphotos%2Fa.112567073917057%2F173648407808923&d=J7URIij%2BjV7QbFiEH5rjuFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=421eaf75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/save12hkyouths/photos/a.112567073917057/173648407808923</a>"},{"pid":"7dade182d7d43c886a5eca4711be8ccceae3cd11","tid":2275841,"uid":280525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a7e40d55c5b500b2e40a63733b9d53a39d5abf9","tid":2275841,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:50:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46836fedf9732cb2984a4af08830b19544422ed2","tid":2275841,"uid":280525,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:50:23.000Z","msg":"加油撐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bebf08ac234c745cc1dbdd4d0849736f8c1233b2","tid":2275841,"uid":76804,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"好多手足本身有女朋友都肯出黎為香港<br />\n唔好再污名化班前線出黎為食女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba17b07ce3f43bc6666d3d6c7d2decf8c2b2eb1e","tid":2275841,"uid":183844,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"bebf08ac234c745cc1dbdd4d0849736f8c1233b2","tid":2275841,"uid":76804,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:50:25.000Z","msg":"好多手足本身有女朋友都肯出黎為香港<br />\n唔好再污名化班前線出黎為食女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:51:37.000Z","msg":"樹大有枯枝<br />\n無偈啦"},{"pid":"d3612f240dd1cd645c206a347429ed7db88abe3f","tid":2275841,"uid":219969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji